Locators


Amazon logo
Search using contains
$x ("//span[contains(@class, 'nav-logo-base')]")


Continue button, search By Id
$x("//input[@id='continue']")

Need help link , search By Class
$x("//span[@class = 'a-expander-prompt']")

Forgot your password link
using By Id
$x("//a[@id ='auth-fpp-link-bottom']")

using Contains
$x("//a[ contains(@ id, 'auth-fpp-link-bottom')]")


Other issues with Sign-In link , By Id
$x("//a[ @id = 'ap-other-signin-issues-link']")

Create your Amazon account button , By And
$x("//a[@id = 'createAccountSubmit' and @class = 'a-button-text']")

Conditions of use link , By Text()
$x("//a[text() = 'Conditions of Use']")

Privacy Notice link , By Text()
$x("//a[text()='Privacy Notice']")
